graph TD
    %% Client Layer
    Client[Client Interface: Web/CLI/Bot] -->|REST API HTTP Requests| Gateway[FastAPI: Application Gateway]

    %% Backend Services
    subgraph FastAPI Backend Services
        Gateway -->|Route: /sessions| SessionSvc[Session Manager]
        Gateway -->|Route: /actions| EngineSvc[Game Engine Service]
        
        EngineSvc -->|1. Fetch State| SessionSvc
        EngineSvc -->|2. Query Context| RAGSvc[RAG Retrieval Service]
        EngineSvc -->|3. Generate Story| LLMSvc[LLM Integration Service]
        EngineSvc -->|4. Update State| SessionSvc
    end

    %% Data Layer
    subgraph Data & State Persistence
        SessionSvc -->|Read/Write State| DB[(PostgreSQL Database)]
        RAGSvc -->|Read Embeddings| VectorDB[(pgvector / Local Cache)]
    end

    %% External APIs
    LLMSvc -->|gRPC/REST| GeminiAPI((Google Gemini API))
    RAGSvc -->|Embedding Generation| GeminiAPI